<https://w3id.org/synapse/amp-als/vocab/diagnostic_criteria> linkml:description "Diagnostic criteria and classification data" .

<https://w3id.org/synapse/amp-als/vocab/differential%20scanning%20calorimetry> linkml:description "Differential scanning calorimetry (DSC) is the measurement of thermodynamic parameters (e.g. enthalpy) during a chemical or biochemical reaction of both a sample and a reference, by the known variation (step-wise or linear) of one variable, whilst a second is kept constant." ;
    linkml:meaning "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHMO_0000684"^^xsd:anyURI .

<https://w3id.org/synapse/amp-als/vocab/differentiated_cell> linkml:description "Differentiated cell type" .

<https://w3id.org/synapse/amp-als/vocab/diffusion%20MRI> linkml:description "MRI method that measure the diffusion of water in the tissue, rather than the content of water as measured in conventional MRI." ;
    linkml:meaning "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/NCIT_C20117"^^xsd:anyURI .

