<https://w3id.org/synapse/amp-als/vocab/light%20scattering%20assay> linkml:description "A method for determining structure by measuring the change in direction or energy of scattered visible light. Light is scattered by the electrons surrounding the atomic nuclei in the sample." ;
    linkml:meaning "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHMO_0000166"^^xsd:anyURI .

