<https://w3id.org/synapse/amp-als/vocab/local%20field%20potential%20recording> linkml:description "An extracellular electrophysiology assay where a microelectrode is placed in the extracellular space of brain tissue to measure action potential and compared to an electrode either outside or inside that tissue." ;
    linkml:meaning "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0002189"^^xsd:anyURI .

