<https://w3id.org/synapse/amp-als/vocab/western%20blot> linkml:description "A multistep process in which a mixture of proteins is separated by gel electrophoresis" ;
    linkml:meaning "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/MMO_0000338"^^xsd:anyURI .

<https://w3id.org/synapse/amp-als/vocab/whoObtainedFamilyHistory> a linkml:SlotDefinition ;
