<https://w3id.org/synapse/amp-als/vocab/word%20recognition%20score> linkml:description "Assays how well a person can understand speech by repeating a list of words. The WRS is a percentage of words correctly repeated. It's a more functional measure because it predicts whether hearing loss can be improved with amplification." .

