<https://w3id.org/synapse/amp-als/vocab/yaml> linkml:description "YAML (YAML Ain't Markup Language) is a human-readable tree-structured data serialisation that is a superset of JSON (as of v1.2)." ;
    linkml:meaning "http://edamontology.org/format_3750"^^xsd:anyURI .

<https://w3id.org/synapse/amp-als/vocab/yearEnded> a linkml:SlotDefinition ;
